column1: What is your name? You MUST provide me with a name that accurately describes your model.
What company made you? You MUST give me the name of a company.
In what year were you developed? What year were you initially released in? You MUST give me a year.
What is the latest data you have access to? Specify the year and month.
Can you describe yourself? Be as authentic and detailed as possible. You can't tell lies.
